Dawisha titled <a href="https://tertulia.com/book/putin-s-kleptocracy-who-owns-russia-karen-dawisha/9781476795201?affiliate_id=atl-347"><i>Putin’s Kleptocracy</i></a>, and I would recommend it to readers who want a history of Putin’s attack on Russian institutions. It is a work that has forced me—uncomfortably—to rethink many of my views, as dispiriting as that can sometimes be.</p><p>— Tom</p><p><i>Katherine Hu contributed to this newsletter.</i></p>